title: Inside a Game
info:
From the nfo:

This is my third Falcon song (10 channels, DHS-Tracker). I had only **3** days to make _anything_ for SillyVenture, so this time it's nothing special - just another dance music. But with some funny 8-bit feeling. ;) 
Surely should be called 'Another non-winning song'. 

Author: YERZMYEY

Title: "Inside a game"

Time: 2:52.

(C) 2012 for Silly Venture 2012 party. 
Atari Falcon 030 MUSIC COMPO. 

1) File: INSIDE.DTM
2) File: Yerzmyey-Inside_a_game.mp3 - an MP3 recorded from real hardware, for all guys who don't own Falcon. 

It's a 10-channels song made on DHS-Tracker (Digital Home Studio).

Computers used: 
Atari Falcon 030 (main work and everything - almost ;) ),
Atari 520ST (for samples),
ZX Spectrum 48K with AY-interface (for samples).

Synthesizers used for samples: 
Yamaha E423

Software: 
Main editor - on Falcon - DHS-Tracker (Digital Home Studio)
MusicMon V2.5e on Atari 520ST (samples-making)
SoundTracker 1.1 on ZX Spectrum 48K (samples-making).
